      "rationale": "FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry used for both validation and COU simulation. Operating envelope (3–6 LPM, 2500–3500 RPM) fully spans COU 5-point test matrix. Gap analysis notes minor impeller blade angle difference (±3°) assessed as negligible at MRL 2. Level 2 met."
